<body style="font-family:Arial, sans-serif; max-width:800px; margin:2rem auto;">
  <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
  <p><strong>Effective Date:</strong> May 2025</p>

  <p><strong>Carsnap Pro</strong> ("we", "our", or "us") is committed to protecting your privacy. This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, and safeguard your information when you use our mobile application, Carsnap Pro, across all supported countries (including USA, UK, UAE, Saudi Arabia, and Kuwait).</p>

  <h2>1. Information We Collect</h2>
  <ul>
    <li><strong>Personal Information:</strong> Name, email address, and phone number (collected during sign-up or login via Firebase Auth).</li>
    <li><strong>User Content:</strong> Uploaded car photos, listing descriptions, and chat messages (stored in Firebase Firestore and Firebase Storage).</li>
    <li><strong>Device Information:</strong> Basic device ID and interaction data (for crash analytics and usage tracking).</li>
    <li><strong>Coarse Location:</strong> Used to show listings by country/city – no precise GPS tracking.</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>2. How We Use Your Data</h2>
  <ul>
    <li>To create and manage user accounts</li>
    <li>To display and manage vehicle listings</li>
    <li>To enable chat between buyers and sellers</li>
    <li>To improve app performance and fix issues (via crash logs)</li>
    <li>To process featured ad promotions (if applicable)</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>3. Data Sharing</h2>
  <p>We do not sell, rent, or share your personal data with third-party advertisers. Data is only shared with trusted services like Firebase and Google Cloud to operate the app securely.</p>

  <h2>4. Data Security</h2>
  <p>All data is transmitted securely using industry-standard encryption (HTTPS/TLS). We rely on Firebase Authentication, Firestore, and Storage, which are protected by Google’s infrastructure.</p>

  <h2>5. Children's Privacy</h2>
  <p>This app is not intended for children under the age of 13. We do not knowingly collect personal information from children.</p>

  <h2>6. Your Rights</h2>
  <p>You can request to view, update, or delete your personal data by contacting us at <strong>ayazkfirm@gmail.com</strong> (or in-app support).</p>

  <h2>7. Changes to this Policy</h2>
  <p>We may update this Privacy Policy periodically. Any changes will be posted within the app and updated on this page.</p>

  <h2>8. Contact Us</h2>
  <p>If you have any questions or concerns, please contact us at:</p>
  <p>Email: <strong>ayazkfirm@gmail.com</strong></p>

  <p>© 2025 Carsnap Pro. All rights reserved.</p>
